295
00:22:02,906 --> 00:22:03,907
{\an8}Sedang apa kau?

296
00:22:03,991 --> 00:22:06,952
{\an8}Ingat, jangan mengerem.

297
00:22:07,035 --> 00:22:08,203
Maaf.

298
00:22:15,127 --> 00:22:17,963
{\an8}Jangan coba-coba! Jangan mengerem.

299
00:22:18,755 --> 00:22:20,174
