dan Charlie Brown mengejar.

353
00:28:10,566 --> 00:28:14,403
Hei, ayo jangan mengerem
dan condong ke tikungan.

354
00:28:14,486 --> 00:28:16,113
Apa kau yakin, Charlie Brown?

355
00:28:16,196 --> 00:28:17,406
Percayalah.

356
00:28:26,832 --> 00:28:27,958
Kita unggul.

357
00:28:32,421 --> 00:28:33,672
Aku tak bisa lihat.

358
00:28:37,801 --> 00:28:42,014
