- Ke mana semua orang?

407
00:32:01,588 --> 00:32:03,674
Kalian menatap apa?

408
00:32:03,757 --> 00:32:05,300
Aku pemenangnya.

409
00:32:11,014 --> 00:32:12,140
Astaga.

410
00:32:15,686 --> 00:32:16,687
Jangan menyerah.

