423
00:33:10,449 --> 00:33:12,201
Itu ide Franklin.

424
00:33:12,284 --> 00:33:13,744
Jika dia tak melakukannya,

425
00:33:13,827 --> 00:33:16,622
kalianlah yang berlumur es krim saat ini.

426
00:33:17,247 --> 00:33:20,250
- Bagus, Franklin.
- Bagus sekali, Charlie Brown.

427
00:33:20,334 --> 00:33:21,502
Hei, kau!

428
00:33:22,711 --> 00:33:25,422
Aku ingin mengatakan satu hal.

429
00:33:26,507 --> 00:33:29,426
Manuvermu cukup berani tadi, Franklin.

430
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:31,595
Kau sungguh menyelamatkan hari.

431
00:33:32,095 --> 00:33:34,932
Piza gratis dariku malam ini.

432
00:33:35,015 --> 00:33:36,767
Maksudku kami.

433
00:33:42,773 --> 00:33:44,191
Aku segera datang.

434
00:33:44,274 --> 00:33:46,193
Orang tuaku mau menemuiku sebentar.

435
00:33:47,027 --> 00:33:48,153
Sampai jumpa nanti malam.

436
00:33:49,071 --> 00:33:52,115
Apa kalian lihat yang kulakukan
bersama temanku Charlie Brown?

437
00:34:19,059 --> 00:34:21,895
Ya, ya, kau mengalahkan kami di sana.

438
00:34:21,978 --> 00:34:23,063
Tetapi lalu kami melebar,

439
00:34:23,146 --> 00:34:25,607
dan kami menyalipmu
dan langsung melewatimu.

440
00:34:25,690 --> 00:34:27,734
Hanya untuk bersiap di tikungan berikut.

441
00:34:28,443 --> 00:34:30,529
Semua termasuk rencana kami.

442
00:34:35,284 --> 00:34:38,620
Franklin, aku senang kau datang.

443
00:34:38,704 --> 00:34:40,998
Hei, Charlie Brown. Maaf aku terlambat.

444
00:34:41,081 --> 00:34:43,833
Orang tuaku mau mengatakan
hal penting kepadaku.

445
00:34:43,917 --> 00:34:47,129
Ayahku menerima pekerjaan baru.
Dan itu berarti...

446
00:34:47,212 --> 00:34:48,839
Kau akan pergi.

447
00:34:50,632 --> 00:34:53,635
